{"tid":2043421,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【美國明尼蘇達示威】共青團中央諷美國騷亂是「美麗風景線」","createTime":"2020-05-30T11:50:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-30T11:57:01.000Z","uid":149978,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"fe5d5b6e80632a39089285d4c98083d0273394e7","tid":2043421,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T11:50:49.000Z","msg":"美國明尼蘇達州（Minnesota）一非裔男子5月25日疑因警員武力拘捕而死亡。事件引發的示威持續，並發生打砸搶等行為。<br />\n<br />\n對於示威者的打砸搶燒行為，5月29日，共青團中央官微在發佈有關明尼蘇達州示威的消息時，用反問的口吻稱「美&hellip;&hellip;美麗的風景線？」，並配上示威地區示威者打砸搶燒的圖片，引發熱議。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B/479413/%E6%98%8E%E5%B0%BC%E8%98%87%E9%81%94%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81-%E5%85%B1%E9%9D%92%E5%9C%98%E4%B8%AD%E5%A4%AE%E8%AB%B7%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E9%A8%B7%E4%BA%82%E6%98%AF-%E7%BE%8E%E9%BA%97%E9%A2%A8%E6%99%AF%E7%B7%9A?utm_source=01appshare&amp;utm_medium=referral\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%2F479413%2F%25E6%2598%258E%25E5%25B0%25BC%25E8%2598%2587%25E9%2581%2594%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E5%25A8%2581-%25E5%2585%25B1%25E9%259D%2592%25E5%259C%2598%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25A4%25AE%25E8%25AB%25B7%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%25A8%25B7%25E4%25BA%2582%25E6%2598%25AF-%25E7%25BE%258E%25E9%25BA%2597%25E9%25A2%25A8%25E6%2599%25AF%25E7%25B7%259A%3Futm_source%3D01appshare%26utm_medium%3Dreferral&d=qJ6fIGaH6M%2FMetNSomypD8jT01h1KCp2%2Bw2KB0oDRGE%3D&h=f4755c63\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B/479413/%E6%98%8E%E5%B0%BC%E8%98%87%E9%81%94%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81-%E5%85%B1%E9%9D%92%E5%9C%98%E4%B8%AD%E5%A4%AE%E8%AB%B7%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E9%A8%B7%E4%BA%82%E6%98%AF-%E7%BE%8E%E9%BA%97%E9%A2%A8%E6%99%AF%E7%B7%9A?utm_source=01appshare&amp;utm_medium=referral</a>"},{"pid":"5de099da687dc0149f6bcb68173a99a45ada31af","tid":2043421,"uid":171668,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T11:52:48.000Z","